description:
On Labor Day Weekend 2010, DJF shared the festival with the world on Jazz Planet.tv -- a streaming news magazine and music channel featuring live and taped performances, news flashes, interviews and behind-the-scenes commentary.

The "planet" went live on opening night with a 30-minute Red Carpet segment hosted by personality extraordinaire Christian McBride interviewing Mayor Dave Bing, Tower of Power's Emilio Castillo, Mulgrew Miller and funders from Chase, DTE Energy and Knight foundations.  

Check out some of the highlights from DJF Jazz Planet!
